These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: indian, colombian, canadian, dutch, chinese, polish, egyptian
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: snowboarding, golf, weightlifting, climbing, sailing, ice-hockey, basketball
 1. the indian is between the dutch and the egyptian##2
 2. the colombian is in the middle##1
 3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 4. the chinese is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person who's sport is sailing##2
 5. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 6. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the dutch##1
 7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person who's sport is climbing and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
 8. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the egyptian##1
 9. the chinese is on the left of the polish##1
10. the chinese is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
11. the polish is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Nationality   | dutch | indian | egyptian | colombian    | canadian | chinese   | polish    |
| Sport         | ice-hockey  | golf   | climbing | snowboarding | weightlifting   | basketball | sailing |

