.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
There 7 different types of food: radish, potato, cranberry, kiwi, broccoli, watermelon, lemon
There are 7 different nationalities: egyptian, malaysian, thai, german, colombian, indian, spanish
1. the indian is on the far left##1
2. the person eating cranberry is between the person eating watermelon and the indian##2
3. the malaysian is on the right of the egyptian##1
4. the person eating lemon is on the right of the thai##1
5. the person eating potato is in the middle##1
6. the colombian is on the left of the egyptian##1
7. the spanish is on the left of the person eating potato##1
8. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the german##1
9. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Food          | broccoli | cranberry | watermelon | potato | lemon | radish      | kiwi  |
| Nationality   | indian | german  | spanish     | thai     | colombian  | egyptian | malaysian |

