.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different nationalities: malaysian, chinese, french, russian, thai, italian, nigerian
7 different pets are kept: goldfish, dog, chinchilla, guinea-pig, snake, horse, bird
 1. the thai is on the left of the malaysian##1
 2. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 3. the owner of the snake is the nigerian##1
 4. the french is on the left of the italian##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 6. the russian is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 7. the malaysian is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 8. the owner of the goldfish is between the owner of the bird and the russian##2
 9. the malaysian is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
10. the chinese is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Nationality   | nigerian | thai | malaysian | chinese   | russian | french | italian |
| Pet           | snake | horse     | dog     | chinchilla | guinea-pig   | goldfish   | bird    |

