.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, hot-chocolate, almond-milk, milk, coffee, cola
There are 7 different nationalities: brazilian, thai, dutch, egyptian, japanese, american, british
 1. the person drinking cola is on the left of the dutch##1
 2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the japanese##1
 3. the american is on the right of the egyptian##1
 4. the person drinking milk is on the right of the japanese##1
 5. the brazilian is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 6. the egyptian is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the american##2
 7. the person drinking 7up is in the middle##1
 8. the egyptian is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 9. the person drinking mirinda is the thai##1
10. the brazilian is the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate    | milk  | almond-milk  | 7up  | cola      | coffee       | mirinda |
| Nationality   | japanese | egyptian | american | british | brazilian | dutch | thai  |

