.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: reggae, funk, techno, indie, hip-hop, salsa, blues
The people use 7 different means of transport: car, snowmobile, jet-ski, boat, roller, taxi, airplane
1. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person driving the roller is the fan of funk##1
3. the person driving the car is between the fan of blues and the fan of reggae##2
4. the fan of salsa is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
5. the person driving the car is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
7. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
8. the person driving the snowmobile is the fan of indie##1
9. the fan of hip-hop is the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Music-Genre   | indie      | hip-hop | reggae | techno | blues      | funk      | salsa |
| Transport     | snowmobile | taxi | airplane       | car | jet-ski | roller | boat |

