.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-6::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  manager, teacher, bartender, architect, musician, freelancer, nurse
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: golf, skateboarding, baseball, sailing, swimming, cricket, basketball
1. the bartender is on the left of the nurse##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is the musician##1
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the teacher is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
5. the freelancer is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
6. the person who's sport is basketball is between the person who's sport is swimming and the manager##2
7. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
8. the freelancer is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| Job     | musician | manager | architect | freelancer | teacher | bartender     | nurse |
| Sport   | baseball   | sailing    | basketball    | swimming      | skateboarding  | golf | cricket |

