.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-7::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: sprite, almond-milk, mirinda, 7up, soy-milk, tea, water
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: ice-hockey, tennis, biathlon, soccer, golf, basketball, swimming
 1. the person who's sport is basketball is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 3. the person who's sport is tennis is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking mirinda is between the person who's sport is golf and the person who's sport is swimming##2
 5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 7. the person who's sport is soccer is the person drinking sprite##1
 8. the person drinking tea is the person who's sport is golf##1
 9. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person who's sport is golf and the person drinking soy-milk##2
10. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Beverage   | sprite | almond-milk    | 7up | mirinda   | tea | water    | soy-milk |
| Sport      | soccer | ice-hockey | swimming    | tennis | golf    | biathlon | basketball  |

