.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-8::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, soy-milk, iced-tea, sprite, 7up, tea
The people have 7 different jobs:  musician, lawyer, nurse, freelancer, analyst, journalist, videographer
 1. the analyst is on the left of the freelancer##1
 2. the musician is on the left of the nurse##1
 3. the journalist is on the far left##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 5. the analyst is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking tea##2
 7. the lawyer is on the right of the journalist##1
 8. the musician is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
10. the person drinking coffee is between the person drinking tea and the person drinking almond-milk##2
11. the analyst is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4     |         5          |     6      |     7     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk  | sprite   | almond-milk         | coffee     | tea              | 7up    | iced-tea     |
| Job        | journalist | lawyer | analyst | freelancer | videographer | musician | nurse |

