.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-9::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: mystery, western, family, sports, comedy, time-travel, fantasy
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, ship, roller, subway, scooter, van, car
1. the person watching mystery movies is the person driving the van##1
2. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is between the person driving the car and the person driving the scooter##2
4. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
5. the person driving the bike is in the middle##1
6. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
7. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
8. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
9. the person driving the car is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3    |    4    |    5     |     6     |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | western | sports     | time-travel | comedy | family | fantasy  | mystery |
| Transport     | roller | subway | scooter   | bike     | car    | ship | van   |

