.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-10::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: juice, water, sprite, lemonade, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, almond-milk
The people have 7 different hobbies: baking, skydiving, card-games, rock-climbing, drawing, writing, reading
1. the person who's hobby is writing is the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking water##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person drinking water##1
4. the person who's hobby is writing is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
5. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
6. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
8. the person drinking lemonade is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person who's hobby is writing##2
9. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |    5    |      6      |    7    |
| Beverage   | water  | juice       | almond-milk         | hot-chocolate         | lemonade   | sprite        | iced-tea |
| Hobby      | reading | card-games | baking | drawing | skydiving | writing | rock-climbing  |

