3. the person who's hobby is photography is in the middle##1
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
5. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person who's sport is golf and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
8. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
9. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |       2       |     3      |       4       |    5    |     6      |       7       |
| Hobby   | collecting | magic-tricks       | sudoku    | photography | gardening | filmmaking     | card-games       |
