.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-12::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: superhero, thriller, disaster, martial-arts, fantasy, romance, comedy
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: electronic, trance, hip-hop, indie, blues, d&b, classical
 1. the person watching superhero movies is the fan of classical##1
 2. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the fan of blues##1
 3. the person watching superhero movies is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the fan of electronic##2
 4. the person watching romance movies is between the person watching comedy movies and the person watching fantasy movies##2
 5. the fan of d&b is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
 6. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 7. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching disaster movies is the fan of blues##1
 9. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
10. the fan of indie is the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3   |   4   |    5    |   6    |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | superhero | thriller  | fantasy   | romance | comedy | disaster |
| Music-Genre   | indie     | classical       | electronic | hip-hop | d&b  | trance   | blues   |

